=head2 C<< replace( $regexp, $replacement ) >>

Operates on C<< $_ >>, which must be a string scalar.

Arguments: B<< Str|RegexpRef >>, B<< Str|CodeRef >>.

Replaces the first regexp match within the string with the replacement string.

