=head2 C<< substr( $start, $length?, $replacement? ) >>

Operates on C<< $_ >>, which must be a string scalar.

Arguments: B<< Int >>, B<< Optional[Int] >>, B<< Optional[Str] >>.

Like C<substr> from L<perlfunc>, but is not an lvalue.

